<br>
Keeping all specializations open would make me feel very eager towards this. Closing off certain paths after you chose one other and I'd hate to see this implemented.<br>
<br>
Of all the damage-dealing classes, wizards are the only ones that can *guarantee* a certain amount of damage.<br>
Not &quot;I can do horrible damage unless the mob has it's toe in the wall&quot;, or unless there's no room in it's back because other melees stood there, or whatever other reason, no: I can *always* do a lot of damage (Okay... unless you don't give me time to med before the fight, but any raid leader can understand that).<br>
